bscr...\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":72,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwiluL2_t-uTAxWhbvIAHaABOFpI_PWBqJ3nr5MTygEExokeYg==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbFlzckU4VEFxU0pUSHRDdk5SUUZIX3FscUhqUXxBQ3Jtc0tsN2JDRlFILXJ0LVNxOG1xRThURUpFWDBSZmxKbXdYZGFZbkxNb1Q0T1RxNUxRbzJHamRVXzg1Q0RabHl1WUE0MVVHbGl5QmVEemFrSkM4dzJOMmNiaGNNX0d1TWp3TDVqWW5LSXNPUnRfcU5ZQkZVOA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=Eya_OdUAevw","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbFlzckU4VEFxU0pUSHRDdk5SUUZIX3FscUhqUXxBQ3Jtc0tsN2JDRlFILXJ0LVNxOG1xRThURUpFWDBSZmxKbXdYZGFZbkxNb1Q0T1RxNUxRbzJHamRVXzg1Q0RabHl1WUE0MVVHbGl5QmVEemFrSkM4dzJOMmNiaGNNX0d1TWp3TDVqWW5LSXNPUnRfcU5ZQkZVOA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=Eya_OdUAevw","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":184,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwiluL2_t-uTAxWhbvIAHaABOFpI_PWBqJ3nr5MTygEExokeYg==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDhtUVRIalprbzZRRV9MbVpkZmhvN3l0RE16d3xBQ3Jtc0tsMnBtOUpTend1MUZVcGdPUG1CYzRFSGNQd01EV2FzaUN4VEZkWTdoRGU2MUlPS2Jpd0t0